Using Docker: 
------------
$> docker run -p 9090:9090 -v /tmp/prometheus.yml:/etc/prometheus/prometheus.yml prom/prometheus

Starting Prometheus from binary:
-------------------------------
$> /home/miltos/go/bin/prometheus --config.file=prometheus.yml

Prometheus should start up. You should be able to browse to a status page at: 
=> http://localhost:9090
=> http://localhost:9090/metrics

